@startuml
autonumber
skinparam boxPadding 10
skinparam participantPadding 10
skinparam style strictuml

title HyperPay "Copy and Pay" Flow (Unified Order & Payment Request)

actor "User" as User
box "Frontend (Next.js)" #E3F2FD
    participant "Payment Page" as NextPage
    participant "Callback Page" as NextResult
end box

box "Backend (Laravel API)" #E8F5E9
    participant "PaymentController" as API
    participant "OrderService" as Service
end box

box "MySQL Database" #FFF8E1
    participant "oc_order" as OrderTB
    participant "oc_hyperpay_payment" as HyperTB
    participant "oc_order_history" as HistoryTB
end box

box "Gateway" #ECEFF1
    participant "HyperPay API" as Gateway
end box

== Phase 1: Order Creation & Checkout Initialization ==

User -> NextPage: Select Payment Method & Click "Proceed"
activate NextPage

NextPage -> API: POST /api/orders/create\n(shipping_address_id, payment_method, etc.)
activate API

API -> Service: createOrder(data)
activate Service
Service -> OrderTB: INSERT INTO oc_order\n(customer_id, status=1 'Pending', total=...)
activate OrderTB
OrderTB --> Service: order_id: 1001
deactivate OrderTB
Service --> API: order object
deactivate Service

API -> Gateway: POST /v1/checkouts\n(entityId, amount, currency, merchantTransactionId=1001)
activate Gateway
Gateway --> API: { "id": "CH-12345-XYZ", "result": {...} }
deactivate Gateway

API -> HyperTB: INSERT INTO oc_hyperpay_payment\n(order_id=1001, checkout_id="CH-12345-XYZ", status="pending")
activate HyperTB
HyperTB --> API: Success
deactivate HyperTB

API --> NextPage: 200 OK\n{ message: "...", data: { order_id: 1001, checkout_id: "CH-12345-XYZ" } }
deactivate API

== Phase 2: Payment Widget (Copy and Pay) ==

NextPage -> NextPage: render HyperPayWidget\ncheckoutId="CH-12345-XYZ", orderId=1001
NextPage -> NextPage: Inject Script\nsrc=".../paymentWidgets.js?checkoutId=CH-12345-XYZ"
NextPage -> User: Display Payment Form (Iframe)
deactivate NextPage

User -> Gateway: Enter Card Data & Submit
activate Gateway
note right of Gateway
    HyperPay processes card.
    3D Secure verification if needed.
end note
Gateway --> User: Redirect to shopperResultUrl\n/checkout/callback?order_id=1001&resourcePath=...
deactivate Gateway

== Phase 3: Payment Verification & DB Update ==

User -> NextResult: Lands on /checkout/callback\n(params: resourcePath, id, order_id)
activate NextResult

NextResult -> API: GET /api/payment/verify\n?resourcePath=...&orderId=1001
activate API

API -> Gateway: GET {resourcePath}\nAuthorization: Bearer Token
activate Gateway
Gateway --> API: { "id": "8a82944a...", "result": { "code": "000.100.110", "description": "Success" }, ... }
deactivate Gateway

alt Payment Successful (Regex match ^000.000.|^000.100.110)

    API -> HyperTB: UPDATE oc_hyperpay_payment\nSET status='paid', payment_id='...', result_code='000.100.110'
    activate HyperTB
    HyperTB --> API: Updated
    deactivate HyperTB

    API -> OrderTB: UPDATE oc_order\nSET order_status_id=5 (Complete/Paid)
    activate OrderTB
    OrderTB --> API: Updated
    deactivate OrderTB

    API -> HistoryTB: INSERT INTO oc_order_history\n(order_id=1001, status=5, comment="Paid via HyperPay")
    activate HistoryTB
    deactivate HistoryTB

    API --> NextResult: 200 OK { success: true, orderId: 1001 }
    NextResult -> User: Redirect -> /checkout/success?order_id=1001

else Payment Failed

    API -> HyperTB: UPDATE oc_hyperpay_payment\nSET status='failed', result_code='...'
    activate HyperTB
    deactivate HyperTB

    API -> OrderTB: UPDATE oc_order\nSET order_status_id=10 (Failed)
    activate OrderTB
    deactivate OrderTB

    API -> HistoryTB: INSERT INTO oc_order_history\n(order_id=1001, status=10, comment="Payment Failed")
    activate HistoryTB
    deactivate HistoryTB

    API --> NextResult: 200 OK { success: false, orderId: 1001, message: "Declined" }
    NextResult -> User: Redirect -> /checkout/failed?order_id=1001

end

deactivate API
deactivate NextResult

@enduml